title: Checkpoint Firewalls: Temperature
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/network/checkpoint
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk

item:
 Name of the temperature sensor.

description:
 This check monitors the temperature sensors in checkpoint firewalls.

 Levels for this check are configurable through the generic "Temperature"
 rule, but please note that this device itself also reports a status which
 may also set a {CRIT} status. You can override this behaviour in the
 "Temperature" rule.

discovery:
 One service is created for each temperature sensor.
